description: Template for collecting metadata about scRNA-seq data.
A template for collecting file-level metadata for scRNA-seq level 3 files including .h5 and tar.gz archives
A template for collecting file-level metadata for scRNA-seq fastq files (i.e., level 1 data).
VEOIBD patient, is a model component
Patient clinical, is a model component
Patient biological entity, is a model component
Patient medication history, is a model component
Patient demographics, is a model component
Metadata files include clinical and biospecimen metadata
An experimental data file that contains data points generated from a single biospecimen. Is a valid value of SpecimenModality that triggers conditional dependencies for other attributes.
